text:
He's banking, has to shift his weight to maintain balance on the board. Notice none of the characters are in static poses, they're all jumping, running, attacking. Even if you've never skateboarded, snowboarded, skied, wakeboarded, etc. you've probably tried a pair of rollerblades or at LEAST ridden a bicycle. Any of these activities require dynamic movement during turns resulting in poses that wouldn't be possible if you were stationary.

TLDR: He's not standing, he's riding.
